{"tid":2239620,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"兵分三路助家屬 鄒家成：冇資格放棄","createTime":"2020-10-12T05:34:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T06:26:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9f2c424a4be630cad7d2b24353a0c3f204ed5c57","tid":2239620,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T05:34:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201012/JILFMYRGNRBKVAJDRRFDA5DQVE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201012%2FJILFMYRGNRBKVAJDRRFDA5DQVE%2F&d=aqHBcmSoErOqRK7CI6xlBWqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=91d6b1e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201012%2FJILFMYRGNRBKVAJDRRFDA5DQVE%2F&h=9d5eb0a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201012/JILFMYRGNRBKVAJDRRFDA5DQVE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n兵分三路助家屬 鄒家成：冇資格放棄<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/WWaPPvMrrie7PWJ5iKljl19X2NU=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NVFCQDO7WFDW5AW4XRGXLGDWWA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FWWaPPvMrrie7PWJ5iKljl19X2NU%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNVFCQDO7WFDW5AW4XRGXLGDWWA.jpg&h=8f37c0de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■朱凱廸（左）及鄒家成（右）堅持協助港青家屬，直言無懼被政權盯上。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】12名涉反修例案件的港青被內地秘密關押近50天，家屬個多月以來奔走營救，民主派也組成支援小隊，兵分多路協助家屬，雖然當中困難重重，但有份協助家屬的鄒家成坦言，他們仍會堅持：「當全部家屬未完全放棄嘅時候，我哋（協助者）都冇資格去放棄。」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：涉收留偷渡者 警扣查30小時  唐婉清保釋：憂12港青安危<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。。，並於短時間內集合12個家庭親屬；由於「港人送中」是民主派從未處理過的課題，故即日碰頭商討，民主派三人支援小隊亦開始行動。<br />\n<br />\n立法會前議員朱凱廸指，營救行動主要兵分三路：鄒家成陪同家屬接受過百中外傳媒訪問，讓香港以致國際社會更了解事件；他主力與航海交通服務業職工會聯絡，並出海尋找中港疑合謀將12人送中的線索；民主黨涂謹申專責與各政府部門交涉，持續向政府施壓。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無懼被跟蹤 料營救以年計<br />\n<br />\n家屬和支援小隊要求合理合法，卻令他們被政權盯上，甚至暴露於危險中。鄒家成透露，自己在跟進12港人事件後常被不明人士跟蹤，某次陪同家屬接受訪問，就有疑似國安人員由早到晚隨他們出行，但他表明會繼與家屬同行：「今日呢個（危險嘅）環境係點都會嚟，個問題係成個協助團隊用咩心態去面對。」<br />\n<br />\n白色恐怖亦阻礙家屬追查真相，朱凱廸曾多次出海尋找線索，惟香港船家一聽聞與12港人有關、從布袋澳出發都拒絕；他們又打電話向有可能目擊12人被捕的希臘貨船船公司查詢，對方都不願多談，「又或者中共係設法令我哋（行動）舉步維艱，佢係千方百計阻止件事水落石出」。<br />\n<br />\n被問到會否擔心因支援而要承擔後果，朱凱廸強調，當中國維權律師在中共壓力下仍堅持接受12港人家屬委託，「另一啲人嘅韌力有幾大、佢哋係點做嘢，我覺得有咗呢啲聯繫，我哋要諗點同佢（中共）鬥長命係多咗好多預備」。鄒家成也預計。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n■記者陳嘉裕"},{"pid":"407b465ff4f3a5c8c78d61827f530a1f9d98c9fb","tid":2239620,"uid":267791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T06:12:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae1c957a4ad2152bfb378bd43f99fad48b6a6b39","tid":2239620,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T06:18:34.000Z","msg":"港共都係想乜都唔認"},{"pid":"3002aefa5cd0ee794e4a6a7fdbd09d34e800a257","tid":2239620,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T06:21:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39ddf11381f2023d342447f44378da7d6f971ddb","tid":2239620,"uid":284429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T06:23:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bcd54f03ab147224ea213e3080584a6e3e2254c","tid":2239620,"uid":243677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T06:24:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb9ef5f4ec0a581bf70bfffddba74c730fee919f","tid":2239620,"uid":195248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T06:25:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"96f3e47f72f74fc18d686ce768add63f8726e122","tid":2239620,"uid":30084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T06:26:30.000Z","msg":"希望家成哥完左呢單野<br />\n唔好痴豬閪咁埋<br />\n驚佢會奶野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}